<chapter id="using" xreflabel="Using">
<title>Examining Nagios Results</title>

<para>
To examine the monitoring data collected by nagios, point your web browser to
the URL:
<screen>
http://localhost/nagios/
</screen>
A window will popup asking for a username and password.
Enter <computeroutput>nagiosadmin</computeroutput> for the username and
the root user's password for the password.
</para><para>
Then you'll see the Nagios web page.
Click on <computeroutput>Host Detail</computeroutput> to see the status
of all the monitored nodes.
</para>

</chapter>
